Summary:
Western Health & Safety Ltd. provides certified asbestos testing and hazardous materials consulting across Alberta and British Columbia. All services are led by Certified Industrial Hygienists (CIHs), ensuring defensible, regulator-ready reporting.

Our team conducts bulk sampling, hazardous materials surveys, and asbestos management plans for construction, demolition, restoration, and insurance-related projects. WHS also performs clearance testing after abatement, delivering formal clearance letters required for re-occupancy.

We serve industries including property management, insurance & restoration, construction, education, and government.

CIHs ensure compliance with Alberta OHS Code, WorkSafeBC Regulation, and WHMIS legislation.

